  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/news/\" rel=\"tag\">科技新闻</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/14/microsoft-and-best-buy-partner-to-create-store-within-a-store/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/microsoft-windows-store-619.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n「店中店」这个概念开始被很多品牌所应用，Microsoft 刚刚宣布他们将会在美加两国超过 600 间 Best Buy 店内开设 Windows Store「店中店」。当中会有 500 间开设在美国 Best Buy，另外 105 间就会在加拿大的 Best Buy 或 Future Shop，它们的大小将会介乎 1,500 至 2,200 平方呎之间，售卖的产品类别包括 Windows 平板、PC、Windows Phone、Office、Xbox 和其他外围产品；他们的专家店员亦会驻场。现在已经有一些开张了啦，预计在 9 月之前就会全部开张。<br />\n </div><p><br /><p class=\"continueReading\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/14/microsoft-and-best-buy-partner-to-create-store-within-a-store/\" rel=\"bookmark\">继续阅读全文 <em>Windows Store「店中店」在 Best Buy 内开张（视频）</em></a></p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/14/microsoft-and-best-buy-partner-to-create-store-within-a-store/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20621778/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/14/microsoft-and-best-buy-partner-to-create-store-within-a-store/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
